    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Hazard uses Jagged Wall to cut off an angle or trap enemies against it, then Violent Leap to close the remaining distance and knock a priority target into his kill zone.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>His wall and leap are both single-target commitments with real cooldowns; whiffing either against a team that just walks around the wall leaves him without a follow-up.</p>"
